- Emotional landscape refers to the mood or set of moods a track can evoke; 
- Versatility in this context means the track is associated with more than one mood;
- The track ID uniquely identifies each track in the album;
- The title represents the name of the album track.

- Classic rockers refers to rock artists in this context;
- Pre-80s albums are those released before January 1, 1980;
- Dominant moods are the most frequent moods among the tracks being considered, limited to the top three.
